the sky slowly begins to darken.

00:01:41.230 --> 00:01:45.280
The many light sources in the game begin to
brighten, to make for a great transition into

00:01:45.280 --> 00:01:46.280
night.

00:01:46.280 --> 00:01:48.960
Once dark, many of the buildings and tents
light up as well.

00:01:48.960 --> 00:01:52.430
